  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6194801">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6194801/" class="title-link">好奇宝宝要珍惜</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6194801"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2020741/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2020741-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2020741/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">只手之鸣</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-08-03"
      class="main-meta">2013-08-03 09:18:54</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6194801_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《所有人问所有人》我是奔着韩寒去的，因为在看《屌丝男士》第二季第一集的时候发现韩寒真的很帅——虽然个头有点儿差强人意。一个个性张扬而又才华横溢的帅哥很难不让我动心，虽然现实中永无交集的可能，但看着书意淫一下也是不错的。  但，《所有人问所有人》并不是韩寒的“...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6194801/#comments">(6回应)</a>
